short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Enhances the Qliksense mashup editor functionalities for better coding experience

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: "Qliksense Mashup Editor Enhancer" is created to help the Qliksense mashup developer who uses QlikSense' inbuilt mashup editor more often.  This extension helps to navigate between your open tabs in with ease and preserves the scroll position. Also provides vertical tab navigator which is much better then the default navigator on the top.
